# Copyrighted source material and raw intermediate transcriptions
# (e.g. PDF excerpts from Brill, Beckerath, and the per-model raw
# transcription outputs). The final reconciled transcriptions and
# derived authority JSON files live under pipeline/pipeline/authority/
# and ARE committed — this repo is private, and those files are
# thin-copyright derivatives. If this repo is ever made public,
# files at pipeline/pipeline/authority/sources/*/reconciled.jsonl
# must be scrubbed first.
proprietary/

# Two-model OCR intermediate outputs (ADR-017). Only the adjudicated
# canonical `raw/page-NNN.md` files are committed per source; the
# per-model scratch and diff reports stay local.
pipeline/pipeline/authority/sources/*/raw/claude/
pipeline/pipeline/authority/sources/*/raw/gemini/
pipeline/pipeline/authority/sources/*/raw/diff/

